label.value: name of reviewing pathologist at organization conducting specimen collection

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who served as the pathologist reviewing a specimen slide at an organization conducting specimen collection from organisms.

label.value: name of data entry person for local pathology review form

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who performed the data entry process for filling in a local pathology review form.

label.value: name of person in gross room receiving OR specimen

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who received a specimen in a pathology gross room from an associated operating room (OR).

label.value: specimen transport from OR to gross room SOP

definition.value: A specimen transport SOP governing the transport of tissue from the operating room (OR) to the pathology gross room.

label.value: name of performer of gross evaluation of resected tissue specimen

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who performed the gross evaluation of a resected tissue specimen.

label.value: additional tumor specimen was obtained and processed with a particular FFPE fixation delay protocol

definition.value: An information content entity that is an indicator of whether a tumor specimen was obtained and processed with a particular FFPE fixation delay protocol other than meeting the top priority for tissue procurement.

label.value: identification number of a protocol at a particular site

definition.value: An centrally registered identifier symbol assigned by an Institutional Review Board (IRB) that identifies a particular protocol at a given site.

label.value: name of person screening specimen donors

definition.value: A personal name that designates who performed the screening of a potential specimen donor for a research study.

label.value: name of person obtaining authorization from legally authorized representative for post-mortem specimen donation

definition.value: A personal name of an individual with research obtainer role who approaches a person's legal representative and informs them of key facts about potential risks and benefits, and asks them for authorization for post-mortem specimen donation  for research for the person they legally represent.

label.value: identifier for legally authorized representative

definition.value: An identifier that uniquely identifies a particular legally authorized representative in a research study.

label.value: relationship between person signing research authorization and specimen donor

definition.value: A relationship that may be biological or legal, between the specimen donor and the legally authorized representative who signed the research authorization.

label.value: time since radiation therapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since radiation therapy prior to surgery.

label.value: time since chemotherapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since chemotherapy prior to surgery.

label.value: time since immunotherapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since immunotherapy prior to surgery.

label.value: time since hormonal therapy was received prior to surgery

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since hormonal therapy prior to surgery.

label.value: lifelong non-drinker of alcohol

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which there is no alcohol consumption.

label.value: current non-drinker of alcohol

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which there was alcohol consumption in the past but is currently a non-drinker of alcohol.

label.value: moderate alcohol consumption history

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which alcohol consumption was equal to or less than 2 drinks per day for men and 1 drink or less per day for women.

label.value: greater than moderate alcohol consumption history

definition.value: An Alcohol Use History in which alcohol consumption was more than 2 drinks per day for men and more than 1 drink per day for women.

label.value: duration of greater than moderate alcohol consumption prior to enrollment

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of greater than moderate alcohol consumption (more than 2 drinks per day for a man or more than 1 drink per day for a woman) prior to study enrollment.

label.value: lifelong non-smoker history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there was no or an insignificant level of smoking.

label.value: current smoker history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there is current smoking either on a daily or non-daily basis.

label.value: current reformed smoker for more than 15 years history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there is no current smoking and has not been smoking for more than 15 years.

label.value: current reformed smoker for less than 15 years history

definition.value: A Smoking History in which there is no current smoking and has not been smoking for less than 15 years.

label.value: duration of hormonal birth control use prior to enrollment

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of use of hormonally based birth control prior to enrollment in a study.

label.value: time since last usage of hormonal birth control

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since the participant last used hormonally based birth control.

label.value: duration of hormone replacement therapy prior to enrollment

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of hormone replacement therapy prior to enrollment in a study.

label.value: time since last usage of hormone replacement therapy

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the time elapsed since the participant last used hormonally replacement therapy.
